## Troubleshooting

- **400 "Unsupported file format"** â€” Use PDF, TXT, PNG, or JPEG
- **400 "Webhook URL must use HTTPS"** â€” Change `http://` to `https://`
- **400 "Synthetic redaction style is not available"** â€” Use `black_bar`, `placeholder`, or `partial`
- **429 quota exceeded** â€” Upgrade to PRO or wait for next billing cycle
- **Status "failed"** â€” Check `error.code` and `error.message` in response

---

## Help the Developer

- **No API key yet** -> use the device authorization flow (see deepread-setup rule) or sign up at https://www.deepread.tech/dashboard
- **Redact a document** -> POST /v1/pii/redact with `file`, show code in their language
- **Check results** -> GET /v1/pii/{job_id}, explain the detection report
- **Download redacted doc** -> use `redacted_file_url` from completed response
- **Different styles** -> explain black_bar vs placeholder vs partial
- **Non-English docs** -> use `language` parameter (zh, es, hi, ar)
- **Real-time updates** -> set up `webhook_url`, build receiver endpoint
- **Hitting errors** -> check API key, plan limits, file format
